Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.28,0:20:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份无法宣泄的绝望感太折磨了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.40,0:20:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西…西撒…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.56,0:20:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.83,0:21:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 西撒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.14,0:21:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马克！
